data.title: Julie Andrews, Rex Harrison win coveted honor
data.meta_description: Photograph caption dated April 6, 1965 reads, "Winner's circle - Julie Andrews, best actress; Rex Harrison, best actor, and Lila Kedrova, best supporting actress, clutch their coveted Oscars after last night's 37th annual Academy Award spectacle in Santa Monica Civic Auditorium."
